def gcf_three_nums(lst):
    def gcd(x, y):
        while(y):
            x, y = y, x % y
        return x

    gcd_num1_num3 = gcd(num1, num3)

    return gcd(gcd_num1_num2, gcd_num1_num3, gcd_num2_num3)
